      <ul>
        <li>Use lists for genuinely list-like content only</li>
        <li>Not as a substitute for proper prose</li>
        <li>Three to five items maximum</li>
      </ul>

      <blockquote>
        <p>Use blockquotes for important principles or distilled insights — not for external quotes.</p>
      </blockquote>

      <h2>What This Means for Your Business</h2>

      <p>Close with something concrete and actionable. Land on a clear takeaway. Do not trail off.</p>

